01:33:22.257 --> 01:33:27.234
Gospodine, gospodine. -Zaustavite tog
čovjeka! -Reacheru! -Zaustavite ga!

01:33:28.870 --> 01:33:30.966
Zaustavite ga!

01:33:31.575 --> 01:33:33.803
Sredite ga, smjesta!

01:33:34.047 --> 01:33:36.374
Duboko udahni, sinko.

01:33:54.155 --> 01:33:56.316
Čisti opijum.

01:34:02.403 --> 01:34:04.797
